       <span class="scomments_info">Mon, 02/10/2014 - 21:41 | <a href="/news/2014-02-10/saxo-bank-ceo-bitcoin-faces-serious-challenges-needs-link-real-assets#comment-4422183" class="active">4422183</a></span>
